One of the provided values in the request query is invalid.
The user is already a team member
The user already requested access to the team
Hobby teams are not allowed to add seats.
The team reached the maximum allowed amount of members, 403: You do not have permission to access this resource.
The authenticated user must be a team owner to perform the action, 404: The team was not found}

@endpoint POST /v1/teams/{teamId}/members/teams/join
